(42, 'default', NULL, 1, 'published', 'kenya', '/kenya', NULL, 'destinations', '{\"title\":\"Kenya\",\"blocks\":[{\"style\":\"style_1\",\"title\":\"Kenya Safari Holidays\",\"description\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Kenya offers some of the finest scenery in East Africa. With famous national parks like the Masai Mara, Amboseli, and Samburu, a vibrant capital city like Nairobi, a white sandy beached coastline along the tropical Indian Ocean, Kenya Safari Holidays are one of the most visited African safari destinations. With wildlife spectacles like the Great Migration to the snow-covered peaks of Africa\\u2019s second-highest mountain Mt Kenya, the Big 5, amazing cultural interactions, and classic Kilimanjaro views, Kenya has an amazing Safari Holidays to offer.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"We have compiled itineraries that incorporate these classic Kenyan safari holidays. Some of our favorite lodges and tented camps are based in Kenya. For an upmarket, exclusive authentic experience Cheli & Peacock operate some beautiful camps like Elsa\\u2019s Kopje in Meru, Joy\\u2019s Camp in Samburu, or the well-known Elephant Pepper Camp in the Mara. &Beyond manage Kichwa Tembo on the banks of the Mara River, the perfect location for the annual Great Migration.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Although the main attraction in Kenya is the big game there is lots of cultural interaction. Lamu Island and the islands off the mainland offer magical beach getaways. Kenya is a classic destination and combines well with Tanzania or Gorilla Trekking in Uganda.\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}],\"text\":\"Why Visit Kenya\"}]},{\"type\":\"bullet_list\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"list_item\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Natural Wonders\"}]}